<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Your Monthly Progress Report</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f7f6;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #2F4F3F;
            color: white;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 24px;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 30px;
        }
        .greeting {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .stats-grid {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .stat-card {
            flex: 1 1 calc(50% - 15px);
            background: #f8faf9;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-left: 4px solid #2F4F3F;
        }
        .stat-label {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .stat-value {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #2F4F3F;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #f8faf9;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #888;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #2F4F3F;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Monthly Progress Report</h1>
            <p>{{monthName}} {{year}}</p>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p class="greeting">Hi {{userName}},</p>
            <p>Great job this month! Here's a summary of your spiritual growth and activity in the app.</p>
            
            <div class="stats-grid">
                <div class="stat-card">
                    <div class="stat-label">Total Reading</div>
                    <div class="stat-value">{{totalReadingMinutes}} mins</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-card">
                    <div class="stat-label">Longest Streak</div>
                    <div class="stat-value">{{longestStreak}} days</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-card">
                    <div class="stat-label">Sessions Completed</div>
                    <div class="stat-value">{{sessionsCount}}</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-card">
                    <div class="stat-label">Top Book</div>
                    <div class="stat-value">{{topBook}}</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <p>Consistency is key to growth. We're excited to see what you achieve next month!</p>
            
            <a href="spiriment://reports" class="button">View Full Details</a>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; {{currentYear}} Spiriment. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
